(35, 'Maramboi Tented Camp', 'maramboi-tented-camp', '<p>Maramboi Tented Camp is ideally located to explore both the Tarangire and Manyara ecosystems.</p><p>An impressive landscape from the Rift Valley gives visitors an amazing natural welcome to an area extraordinarily rich in wildlife. The camp offers stunning views of the Manyara National Park, Rift Valley, Ngorongoro highlands and on clear days even Oldonyo Lengai – a sacred Masai mountain.</p><p><br /></p><p>At camp there are 40 spacious tents built on ample wooden decks. 26 of the tents are standard rooms and there are 2 units that interconnect, which are perfect for families. In addition to these there are 10 suites which offer a bit more in the way of technical amenities such as wifi, plus all drinks are included. All tents have en-suite facilities and a private veranda and each is supplied with mains electricity.</p><p><br /></p><p>There is a good sized swimming pool at the camp, plus a mess tent where meals are served, a library and reception where a cell phone is always available.</p><p>In the wet season the Manyara and Tarangire pans fill with water which attracts huge flocks of flamingos and wading birds.</p><p>At Maramboi the lay of the land is such that view of the great migration is often unobscured by trees, meaning that guests can watch it from their tents at certain times of the year.</p>', 21.023985, 105.791488, NULL, '12', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '198', '200,199,198,196,197,195,194,193', NULL, NULL, 3, '', '', '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'off', 5, '', '68', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'on', 1, 'publish', '2022-10-23 08:44:08', '2022-10-23 08:49:33', 'enquiry', 'off', NULL, '', NULL),
