(9, 'Privacy Policy', 'privacy-policy', '<p>Tanzania Safaris takes your privacy seriously and will not disclose your personal details to any other parties you have not authorized them to be passed to.</p><p>The Privacy Policy below outlines how Tanzania Safaris uses the personal information that you provide: Name, address, email address and telephone number. When you register with Tanzania Safaris or send a holiday inquiry, you consent to the collection and use of this information in the ways described below. Tanzania Safaris does reserve the right to update these so please visit this page occasionally.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>What Information do we collect?</strong></p><p>When you send in a holiday inquiry, newsletter sign up or brochure request, we ask for that personal data necessary to fulfill the request. This information can be any or all of: Name, Address, Telephone and/or email address.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>What do we do with it?</strong></p><p>We use the information to perform the request for which you sent it. We will also use it to notify you of special offers that we believe may be of interest to you and when our new newsletter is available. There is an opt-out when you send your information initially and on all subsequent occasions that we contact you.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Internet collected information</strong></p><p>When you visit the Tanzania Safaris site we automatically collect certain information: Search terms used to find our site on search-engines, the site you came from, the length of visit, the pages you visited, the type of browser you use. None of this information is linked to your identity. It is gathered anonymously to help understand our site and to make improvements to help you, the visitor.</p>', '', 'publish', 1, '2021-02-01 02:40:37', '2022-12-16 09:38:10', NULL),
