(14, 'Tanzania Safaris Careers', 'careers', '<h2>Work for us</h2><p>Tanzania Safaris<span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> is an adventure travel company based in Tanzania. For over 10 years we’ve been offering enriching travel experiences internationally and domestically. Our team is passionate and committed to our guests, our company, and the communities in which we operate</span>. We are always on the look out for candidates with a real passion for Africa, as well as seasoned senior Tanzania consultants.</p><p><br></p><h4>Current Vacancies</h4><p><br></p><h5>Travel consultant</h5><p><br></p><p><strong>About the Job</strong></p><p>As a Travel consultant, you’ll work with qualified leads to create one-of-a-kind travel experiences. From the first phone call to the official booking, you’ll be there to guide them through the planning process. You’ll help answer questions, determine destinations, select itineraries, and get guests excited to take their dream trip with Tanzania Safaris!</p><p><br></p><p><strong>About You</strong></p><p>You’re a people person! You don’t shy away from phone conversations and you love to help. You consider yourself a planner, are highly organized, and goal-oriented. You’re creative and a hard worker, and enjoy being around people with those same qualities. You can be independent and driven, and supportive team player at the same time. You’re ready to learn about new places and share that knowledge with discerning guests.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Become a destination expert after training with fellow team members</li><li>Connect with guests and build relationships with phone calls and emails</li><li>Engage with new and long-term leads from our company database</li><li>Create and send itineraries and proposals for both standard and customized trips</li><li>Coordinate with our international partners to confirm trip itineraries</li><li>Collect details and payment to book and confirm guests’ itineraries</li><li>Meet and exceed sales targets and team goals</li><li>Work to continually refine and improve our product and brand image</li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Exceptional phone manner</li><li>Exemplary written and oral communication skills</li><li>Finely tuned time-management and organizational abilities</li><li>Able to adapt and learn on the fly, while knowing when to ask for help</li><li>Familiarity with MS Office, especially Excel and Outlook</li><li>Experience using database software (bonus points for experience with FileMaker!)</li><li>Minimum three years sales experience</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>Please send your CV and covering letter to info@tanzania-safaris.com.</p>', '', 'publish', 1, '2022-10-01 09:32:16', '2022-12-16 04:58:30', NULL),
(15, 'About Tanzania Safaris', 'about-us', '<p>Tanzania-safaris.com is a registered tour operator and travel agency in Tanzania, powered by an enthusiastic team with vast experiences working in the Tourism and Hospitality Industry in Tanzania for more than 10 years. Our shared admiration for professional and world class customer service inspired us to form this travel company. Competing in a fiercely competitive market, we believe that being a small company run by a lean team is our biggest strength. We can afford to focus and be more detail-oriented and personalize our service delivery for all our valued guests building relationship and friendship along the way.</p><p><br></p><h2>Why Tanzania Safaris?</h2><p>Because most people don’t know much about Tanzania and haven’t the slightest clue on how to get to tanzania, interested and curious travelers often fall victim to exorbitant prices charged by overseas agents to travel to Tanzania. As a responsible stakeholder in the Tourism Industry of Tanzania, we feel that these unethical practices should be stopped in favor of the travelers and for the reputation of the destination as well.</p><p><br></p><p>Therefore at Tanzania Safaris, our mission is to provide accurate and relevant information regarding Tourism in Tanzania directly to the end customers eliminating business entities in between. We promote transparent pricing and assist our guests plan their trip to Tanzania as hassle free as possible. Our website also features a comprehensive travel guide and extensive coverage of information on Tanzania including top attractions and experiences in Tanzania to offer our customers a preview of what to expect on their trip to Tanzania.</p><p><br></p><p><strong><em>Discerning travelers are always looking for the authentic local experience wherever they travel to. Would you rely on a foreign agent who has probably never even visited Tanzania or at best a few times and claims to know everything about the destination or would you rather have a local expert plan your trip to deliver that true local experience.&nbsp;</em></strong></p><p><br></p><h2>What We Offer?</h2><p>With our extensive knowledge about Tanzania coupled with our expertise in tour management, we offer both pre-designed tour packages and tailor made travel itinerary for groups and individual travelers as per your preferences and interest. During the discussion, we offer suggestions and guidance to address concerns ensuring our guests are satisfied with the pre-travel planning. Our services also include hotel and flight reservations, arrangement of guide, land transport and most importantly the visa processing formalities.</p><p><br></p><p>Known for our high standards of quality and attention to detail, we have helped tourists go back home with great memories of their trip to Tanzania. Tanzania Safaris has been organizing inbound tours to Tanzania for more than 10 years.</p>', '71', 'publish', 1, '2022-10-11 04:37:00', '2022-11-11 06:33:30', NULL),
