(18, '10 Best Kilimanjaro Tour Companies 2023: Reviewed', 'best-kilimanjaro-tour-companies', '', '<h1>10 Best Kilimanjaro Tour Companies 2023: Trekking Operators Reviewed</h1>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Mount Kilimanjaro is one of the most attractive places for ordinary tourists and climbers from all over the world. Climbing Kilimanjaro, the highest African peak, can be the most memorable adventure of your life. To make your Kilimanjaro dream a reality, you must carefully approach choosing the right tour operator. This is the most important step because you need to trust them for climbing safety and summit success. When choosing a tour operator, we advise you to pay attention to reviews by tourists on the popular resources for travelers, like Tripadvisor, Lonely Planet, or other Travel guides. Always notice the public reputation of the company.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../storage/2022/12/13/best-kilimanjaro-companies-1670901592.jpg\"/></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Key Factors in Evaluating a Climbing Tour Operator</h2>\r\n<p>As you can see, the most comfortable way to step on the top of Kilimanjaro is provided by the climb operators. You need a company that specializes in extreme recreation. When you make your choice, you should be guided by these criteria:</p>\r\n<h3>Focus on Safety</h3>\r\n<p>You should remember that climbing Kilimanjaro is a dangerous process when it comes to altitude sickness. Make sure that your chosen tour operator provides professional guides with mountain rescue qualification and at least two years of experience.</p>\r\n<h3>Clients&rsquo; Success Rate</h3>\r\n<p>Explore the clients&rsquo; success rate of your tour company. Remember not only to check Kilimanjaro trekking companies&rsquo; websites, but also use web resources popular with tourists from all over the world, like TripAdvisor. There you can not only find some useful reviews but also ask questions about the company you&rsquo;ve chosen.</p>\r\n<h3>Quality Gear</h3>\r\n<p>Quality equipment is one of the key parts of the climbing process. It must always be provided by responsible hiking operators. The most important camping and climbing equipment includes tents, oximeters, and oxygen systems (at that height in the air there is little oxygen, but it will be stored in the cylinders).</p>\r\n<h3>Private and Group Climbs</h3>\r\n<p>Remember that the best Kilimanjaro operators provide different privacy options for climbing trips. You can always choose a private climb only to share this experience with your friends.</p>\r\n<h3>Meals</h3>\r\n<p>Budget tour operators typically only provide simple carbohydrates such as rice, pasta, and porridge, because at higher altitudes, these are assumed to be easier to digest. For most meals, operators should aim to include a variety of foods and a decent ration of fruit and vegetables as well as protein.</p>\r\n<h3>Overall Quality Services</h3>\r\n<p>Don&rsquo;t forget to check if there is a special porter in the climbing crew provided by your tour operator. A porter helps to carry your things during the climb and provides camping equipment. When climbing Kilimanjaro, you will cross several climate zones, traveling from summer to winter and back again.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../storage/2022/12/13/mount-kilimanjaro-companies-1670902350.jpg\"/></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Tour Operator Experience</h3>\r\n<p>Regarding many of these circumstances, we advise you to choose the most experienced tour operator. The oldest and most well-experienced ones will provide more sophisticated help and a professional climbing crew.</p>\r\n<h3>Tour Operators Popular with Celebrities</h3>\r\n<p>Don&rsquo;t forget to check some popular bloggers and celebrity Instagram pages to check out photos and videos of their Kilimanjaro climb programs.</p>\r\n<p>Besides the inspiration, you also can learn some useful and relevant information on interesting Kilimanjaro trips provided by the responsible tour operators.</p>\r\n<h2>Top 10 Best Kilimanjaro Tour Companies</h2>\r\n<p>Here&rsquo;s our top of companies that organize best trips to the mount Kilimanjaro:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>1. Climbing Kilimanjaro</h3>\r\n<p>A clear winner of our Top 10 is <a href=\"https://www.climbing-kilimanjaro.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Climbing Kilimanjaro</a>. First of all it&rsquo;s the only Kilimanjaro company that has its own guiding school. They train their guides all year round. The school also offers classes to other guides from different companies. Their intention is to make Kilimanjaro the &ldquo;safest Mountain to climb in the world.&rdquo;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Experience: They guide more clients on the Mountain more than any other company making them the most experienced climbing operator on the mountain. They have been operating in Tanzania for more than 15 years. While Kilimanjaro is clearly the focus of their activity, they can also supplement your climbing experience with a safari adventure or beach holidays on one of the Tanzanian islands.</p>\r\n<p>Safety: Safety is Climbing Kilimanjaro\'s number one priority. Dedicated to client safety, they conduct two daily health checks throughout the climb to detect the onset of the altitude sickness before it progresses to a dangerous stage. All of their guides are certified Wilderness First Responders, yearly retrained and re-examined on their professional knowledge. You can read in depth about <a href=\"https://www.climbing-kilimanjaro.com/kilimanjaro-safety/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Kilimanjaro Safety</a>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>High Success Rate: Climbing Kilimanjaro They have the highest summit record than any other Kilimanjaro Company and this is due to the fact that the service they offer is top notch. All of their Wilderness First Responder certified guides have over 50 summits under their belts. So they know the Mountain like the back of their palms.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To sum it up, Climbing kilimanjaro is the Best Kilimanjaro Company they have better guides, better equipment, and better meals than their competitors.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Check out Climbing Kilimanjaro Day to day real time trek updates from Mount Kilimanjaro : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/climbingmtkilimanjaro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Climbing Kilimanjaro Facebook</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Climbing Kilimanjaro hold 5/5 rating on TripAdvisor. : <a href=\"https://www.tripadvisor.com/Attraction_Review-g13345721-d16849488-Reviews-Climbing_Kilimanjaro-Machame_Kilimanjaro_Region.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">&nbsp;Climbing kilimanjaro Tripadvisor Reviews</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../storage/2022/12/13/climbing-kilimanjaro-best-companies-1670902936.jpeg\"/></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>2. Tanzania Expeditions</h3>\r\n<p>Tanzania Expeditions stands apart as one of the top-rated, fairly-priced local operators conducting the best Kilimanjaro tours. They have been conducting Kilimanjaro treks for more than 7+ Years.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>They provide Kilimanjaro trekking packages, Safaris and Zanzibar vacations for clients across the world, and specialize in customizing packages for individuals too.</p>\r\n<p>They offer many tips and tricks on their<a href=\"http://tanzania-expeditions.com/climbing-kilimanjaro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> </a><a href=\"http://tanzania-expeditions.com/climbing-kilimanjaro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">website</a> on how to best make it up the mountain and how to prepare prior to your hike.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>3. Pristine Trails.&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p>They pride themselves as a top-rated company serving hundreds of travelers each year. Their&nbsp;focus is tailor-made tours with a responsible approach, personalized and enriching experiences for the traveler while also benefiting the local people, wildlife and conservation efforts of the country.</p>\r\n<p>Edward Lyimo who&rsquo;s the founder was born and raised in Tanzania. He is a wildlife enthusiast with a degree in African Wildlife Management and more than 15 years in the tourism industry.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Pristine Trails TripAdvisor rating is 5/5.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>4. Summit Africa</h3>\r\n<p>Summits Africa LTD is based in northern Tanzania. They&nbsp;have partners in Uganda, Kenya, Rwanda, Ethiopia and the Democratic Republic of Congo for fulfilling programs across the region.</p>\r\n<p>They are a core team of guides &amp; crew providing white label solutions to the travel industry from porter management all the way up to highly customized total event management solutions.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>5. Kandoo Adventures</h3>\r\n<p>Kandoo Adventures create life-changing experiences through adventure travel that have a positive impact on individuals and the communities they visit. As part of the Alta&iuml; Travel family, they operate trips with a personal hands-on approach, ensuring clients have an excellent experience throughout their journey.</p>\r\n<p>Kandoo Adventures is a well-known Kilimanjaro climbing operator being on track for ten years already. The company is famous for precise attention to any aspects of the climbing trip.</p>\r\n<p>5/5 on TripAdvisor.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>6. Ultimate Kilimanjaro</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;Ultimate Kilimanjaro, offers high quality service on their Climbs. They have a good track record, high ratings and plenty of experience. Ultimate Kilimanjaro has been in operation for 10 + years They prioritizes client safety with mandatory twice-a-day medical checks for all climbers, and guides trained as Wilderness First Responders. And also offer scheduled group and private climbs.</p>\r\n<p>Ultimate Kilimanjaro TripAdvisor rating is 5/5.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>7. Tusker Tails</h3>\r\n<p>Tusker Trail is one of the established companies on this list. As one of the original Kilimanjaro companies, Tusker Trail has been a leader in the industry for quite some time.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>All of their guides have comprehensive medical training and experience hiking up the mountain. Tusker Trails also makes sure that there are plenty of guides per group, usually ranging from two to six guides per group.</p>\r\n<p>Tusker Trails Rating on Tripadvisor&nbsp;is 4/5.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>8. Peak Planet</h3>\r\n<p>Though Peak Planet is headquartered in the United States, They book clients from all over the world including Canada, Australia, New Zealand, United Kingdom and other parts of Europe.</p>\r\n<p>Their Kilimanjaro specialists are highly knowledgeable about all facets of climbing Kilimanjaro and they are one of the few specialist companies with a long track record of organizing high-quality Mount Kilimanjaro climbs.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Peak Planet Rating on Tripadvisor&nbsp;is 4/5.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>9. Team Kilimanjaro</h3>\r\n<p>Team Kilimanjaro mountain staff are divided into close-knit teams each led by a chief guide who reports daily from the mountain, directly their Expedition Coordinator.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>They offer a wide variety of tips for climbing the mountain on their website. Along with this, they give you recommendations on how to prepare for your climb. Each team has a chief guide with a team to assist a group of climbers. They have a wide variety of guides available and have a page dedicated to their founders. Their two founders both have or do still hold records for climbing Mount Kilimanjaro the fastest in the UK.</p>\r\n<p>Team Kilimanjaro Rating on Tripadvisor&nbsp;is 4/5.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>10. Easy Travel</h3>\r\n<p>Easy Travel offers Safaris and treks to kilimanjaro.Their staff is a tightly woven team dedicated to welcoming every guest into Tanzania and crafting the most life-changing experiences possible.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Having operated as a family-run business for 35 years, Easy Travel has experience, but importantly, They continue to have experiences that they constantly learn from. Each year, they set out to improve on the last, using their gained experience to provide the best possible trip for clients.</p>\r\n<p>In our 35 years, they claim to have combed over each square kilometer of Tanzania, and know exactly how to lead a tour up Kilimanjaro, find the best spots to see wild animals in national parks, and when to hit the beautiful beaches of Zanzibar.</p>\r\n<p>Easy Travel&nbsp;Rating on Tripadvisor&nbsp;is 4/5.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>What Should Your Operator Organize Before the Climb?</h2>\r\n<p>Conquering Kilimanjaro is not a simple tourist trip, so your chosen operator is obliged to give you a list of recommendations before you go on the trip. First, the company should be concerned with your health and safety: what vaccinations to do before the trip, how to choose the right equipment and backpack, and what medications can help with acclimatization.</p>\r\n<p>Your trek operator in Kilimanjaro will arrange nearly everything you need to climb Kilimanjaro locally. Together with guides, cooks, and porters, they will recruit your mountain crew, provide full meals and drinking water. They will also arrange your mountain accommodation, arrange transfers to the gates of the park, and work out fees and regulations for your park entry.</p>\r\n<p>Your operator will arrange your airport transfers and book your accommodation before and after your trip, depending on your package. They can also help you organize equipment, such as sleeping bags or trekking poles, which you may prefer to rent rather than buy.</p>\r\n<p>Tour operators are government-controlled and are required to maintain appropriate licenses to run tours up Kilimanjaro. Ask your company to provide copies of these documents for confirmation.</p>\r\n<h2>Things to Remember When Planning A Kilimanjaro Trip</h2>\r\n<p>Summing up, it is important to mention the basic rules of choosing the right guide company to conquer the Kilimanjaro summit.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Do not try to save money: cheap tours can harm your health and mood</li>\r\n<li>Learn about the experience of the company you are interested in and be sure to check the reviews of tourists on different social networks</li>\r\n<li>Do not forget to prepare your body for Kilimanjaro climbing, then the experience will be truly magical, and you will get truly inspired.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Here are the Top 3 companies to climb Kilimanjaro we recommend in 2023:</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Climbing Kilimanjaro</li>\r\n<li>Tanzania Expeditions</li>\r\n<li>Pristine Trails</li>\r\n</ol>', '', '', '217', 'publish', 1, '2022-12-03 10:17:22', '2022-12-23 05:20:17', NULL),
